content.p: SNS is a high speed internet link for students living in the halls of residences of The University of Nottingham Malaysia Campus. All campus halls have access points that broadcast WLAN connection to the residents. To connect: For Android/iPhone/iPad devices, follow the instructions below: *Note: Find 3 & 4 hidden under Advanced options if available Having trouble getting connected? If you require assistance with SNS, please contact: telephone: +603 8924 8199 fax: +603 8924 8007 email: itservicedesk@nottingham.edu.my
